                      <span>0</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2000-03-24</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>India Style is a timely and refreshing look at one of the oldest civilizations in the world. India 'style' relfects the complexity and depth found in Indian cooking. Similar to how spices are blended and prepared, the country's style is a vibrant blending of color, texture, culture, religion and history. India style has been developing for thousands of years. There is something within our soul that responds and reaches out to this richness.</span>
                  
              
